3335" target="_blank" data-eid="qd_A108" data-bid="1016533335">我真是非洲酋长</a></h3><p>纵横国际动保组织拉赞助，持枪对战各国偷猎队，清扫想来占便宜的帮派势力，这里是非洲，这是我的地盘！</p><a class="read-btn" href="//book.qidian.com/info/1016533335" target="_blank" data-eid="qd_A109" data-bid="1016533335">书籍详情</a></div><div class="desc-wrap item2" data-rid="2"><h3><a href="//book.qidian.com/info/1016660823" target="_blank" data-eid="qd_A108" data-bid="1016660823">我的徒弟都是大反派</a></h3><p>大徒弟幽冥教教主手下万千魔众，二徒弟剑魔一言不合就开杀戒……</p><a class="read-btn" href="//book.qidian.com/info/1016660823" target="_blank" data-eid="qd_A109" data-bid="1016660823">书籍详情</a></div><div class="desc-wrap item3" data-rid="3"><h3><a href="//book.qidian.com/info/1016989332" target="_blank" data-eid="qd_A108" data-bid="1016989332">重生之我是大空头</a></h3><p>金融精英沈建南因为开车穿越到九十年代成了大学老师，靠着歪曲的理论教出了一堆歪脖子树。</p><a class="read-btn" href="//book.qidian.com/info/1016989332" target="_blank" data-eid="qd_A109" data-bid="1016989332">书籍详情</a></div><div class="desc-wrap item4" data-rid="4"><h3><a href="//book.qidian.com/info/1010327039" target="_blank" data-eid="qd_A108" data-bid="1010327039">三寸人间</a></h3><p>举头三尺无神明，掌心三寸是人间。</p><a class="read-btn" href="//book.qidian.com/info/1010327039" target="_blank" data-eid="qd_A109" data-bid="1010327039">书籍详情</a></div><div class="desc-wrap item5" data-rid="5"><h3><a href="//book.qidian.com/info/1018180913" target="_blank" data-eid="qd_A108" data-bid="1018180913">赛博英雄传</a></h3><p>重开天地自成体系的赛博武道初祖向山，念着仇敌的名字醒了过来。</p><a class="read-btn" href="//book.qidian.com/info/1018180913" target="_blank" data-eid="qd_A109" data-bid="1018180913">书籍详情</a></div><div class="desc-wrap item6" data-rid="6"><h3><a href="//book.qidian.com/info/1015609210" target="_blank" data-eid="qd_A108" data-bid="1015609210">明天下</a></h3><p>明末的历史纷乱混杂，堪称是一段由一些有着强大个人魅力的人书写成的历史。</p><a class="read-btn" href="//book.qidian.com/info/1015609210" target="_blank" data-eid="qd_A109" data-bid="1015609210">书籍详情</a></div><div class="desc-wrap item7" data-rid="7"><h3><a href="//book.qidian.com/info